column4: Our Performance Sports Bra is made from CS Contour Lycra and is designed to be the ultimate multipurpose piece for women who demand a technical high-support bra. The best part?  It can be fully customized with virtually any design using our digital sublimation printing process.

column1: Apex Men's Run Top (V Neck Design)
column4:
The Champion System Apex Run Top is constructed of our exclusive CS AirLite fabric with strategically placed mesh side panels for even greater breathability and flatlock seams for increased comfort. A must for training and competition.


Features:



  • Constructed of CS AirLite fabric.

  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+.

  •  No annoying label tags at the neck

  • Fully customisable. 

  • Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more.

The Champion System Technical Performance Top is designed to maximize your workout by keeping you dry and comfortable.  Made from our exclusive microfiber CS Tech fabric, the Performance Run Top offers the fit and feel you demand from your performance clothing.


Features:

  • Constructed of CS Tech fabric
  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+
  • No annoying label tags at the neck
  • Fully customisable
  • Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more

When Summer runs into Autumn and Autumn runs into Winter this lightweight water-resistant jacket will be your go to run jacket that can do it all.


Features


  • Constructed of CS WindGuard. Lightweight, water-resistant and breathable to help keep your temperature regulated
  • Draw cord that makes fine-tuning the fit easy
  • Reflective details help with low light visibility
  • Offset zipper with zipper garage to help keep your chin from getting chafed
  • Secure front zipper pockets, one with media pouchand a cord exit for your headphones,the other has an interior credit card-size Velcro pocket for convenience.
  • Elastic cuffs
  • Mesh venting in the back and the under arms to reduce over-heating
